23/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake)</a>公开了新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/n-sync">*NSYNC</a>曲目，该曲目是由新重组的乐队于本周早些时候宣布的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/justin-timerlake-man-woods-review-2230941">贾斯汀·汀布莱克——《林中人》评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲是他们 20 多年来的第一首新歌，名为“Better Place”，这支著名的九十年代男孩乐队将再次重聚。</p><p>这个由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake</a> )、克里斯·柯克帕特里克 (Chris Kirkpatrick)、JC Chasez、乔伊·法通 (Joey Fatone) 和兰斯·巴斯 (Lance Bass) 组成的男孩乐队于周二（9 月 12 日）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-2023-mtv-vmas-3496804">2023 年 MTV VMA</a>上重聚<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nsync-reportedly-set-to-reunite-at-2023-vmas-3496818">，并为泰勒·斯威夫特颁奖</a>。</p><p>在此之前，该乐队的回归歌曲在第三部<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/trolls-film-review-1652915"><em>《魔发精灵》</em></a>电影<em>《魔发精灵乐队》</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nsync-appear-to-be-teasing-reunion-single-for-new-trolls-movie-3492732">海报上被调侃</a>。宣传片以 *NSYNC 标志为特色，并通过二维码引导粉丝访问包含音乐片段的<a href="https://www.takeyoutoabetterplace.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站</a>。</p><p>从那时起，汀布莱克就在 Instagram 上分享了这首歌的制作幕后花絮，以及他如何向其他 *NSYNC 成员推销这个想法。“这么多明星齐心协力……如果我们制作这首歌，那就是一种爱给我们粉丝的一封信，”汀布莱克告诉他们。 “我很荣幸能邀请乐队来演唱这首歌。”</p><p> “当星星对齐时......让我的兄弟们回到工作室一起做一些有趣的事情，能量很特别，”汀布莱克在视频的标题中写道。 “《更好的地方》将于 9 月 29 日推出。爱你们。”</p><p>您可以在这里观看该剪辑： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CxLzQ19vj8h/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 